{"tid":35801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼馬戲團虐待海豚 塞入木箱迫跳火圈","createTime":"2016-12-12T10:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T11:42:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8f9d5eb802a897693f95753f466a109e86c7ce","tid":35801,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YW4Lw7PoCy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYW4Lw7PoCy8&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=95162c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YW4Lw7PoCy8</a><br />\n<br />\n印尼一個巡迴馬戲團被揭發強迫海豚表演跳火圈，有部份海豚缺乏適當照料及飽受壓力而死亡。<br />\n<br />\n慈善組織「海豚計劃」（Dolphin Project）公開有關片段，可見海豚要在水池中跳火圈，還要以魚鰭捧&amp;#30528;籃球「背泳」等，當中兩隻海豚在表演時犯錯，工作人員用大鐵棒拍打水面嚇牠們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/dolphin_U14lN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fdolphin_U14lN_1200x0.png&h=8ff4f73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n表演結束後，身長6呎的海豚更被放入注滿水、但無法轉身的窄小木箱中，與其他動物一起用貨車運走。<br />\n<br />\n「海豚計劃」成員奧巴里（Ric O&rsquo;Barry）說：「這（對海豚）非常殘忍，這是我唯一一次看到海豚跳火圈。絕對只會在過去的時代發生。」他又指，這些馬戲團長年遊走各地，由於沒有適當的飼養設施，這或會加劇海豚被虐待的情況。<br />\n<br />\n巡迴馬戲團在印尼大受歡迎，「海豚計劃」估計目前有72條海豚被非法捕獲，分別在3個馬戲團中表演。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》/《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"7f04a30e8a74068c1313831de2fa2a0947186fea","tid":35801,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d62e90e6d186bcb2ab2e03678339ea7c414e8","tid":35801,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"fucking indogs"},{"pid":"20161cd491504d41fe343beda085892c0e91cadb","tid":35801,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"去大陸睇過一次之後好撚憎睇馬戲團<br />\n動物園都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}